  <bioghist id="aspace_0d8192df587e31e12fde80fa27d942f5">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Vice President for Research, Cornell University; president, Cornell Aeronautical Laboratory; president, Cornell Research Foundation; chairman of the executive committee, Cornell-Guggenheim Aviation Safety Center; chairman, Cornell Committee for Transportation Safety Research.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_f602decc91d7e0f7d76322a58ee89bc6">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes Cornell Aeronautical Laboratory correspondence; pamphlets, correspondence, photographs, reports, and clippings concerning aviation; and other papers reflecting Wright's career in aviation and at Cornell University. Also, four bound volumes of Theodore P. Wright's articles and addresses, 1918-1970.</p>  </scopecontent>
